70
00:10:10,280 --> 00:10:14,240
No, no, no. No, you love me.
It's a Martin Taylor fact.

71
00:10:14,280 --> 00:10:18,702
Has there been a day in the last five years
that we haven't talked?

72
00:10:19,240 --> 00:10:23,240
