what you've just said to me on tape,

972
01:30:16,200 --> 01:30:19,170
with a solicitor and your parents present.

973
01:30:22,680 --> 01:30:24,480
Why?

974
01:30:24,520 --> 01:30:27,160
Your statement needs to be official.

975
01:30:27,200 --> 01:30:30,640
–I'm not making a statement.
–You have to.

976
01:30:30,720 --> 01:30:35,000
That's what the families and everybody
—the police—have been waiting for.

977
01:30:35,040 --> 01:30:38,800
I just told you:
they're not going to understand.

978
01:30:39,480 --> 01:30:42,240
Look, even you don't understand.

979
01:30:42,280 --> 01:30:46,320
I don't see why I should be punished.
It was an accident!

980
01:30:46,360 --> 01:30:49,760
–You're still responsible.
–I'm not ruining my life for this!

981
01:30:49,800 --> 01:30:54,240
It's out of your hands. Martin will
corroborate what you've told me.

982
01:30:54,280 --> 01:30:58,280
Everyone is dead,
and you told them that I locked you in!

983
01:30:58,920 --> 01:31:03,680
I was away!
I had no idea you couldn't get out!

984
01:31:10,560 --> 01:31:12,520
It's too late.

985
01:31:21,360 --> 01:31:23,560
No!

986
01:31:26,440 --> 01:31:30,520
–Philippa! What the fuck are you doing?
–Help! Help!

987
01:31:31,000 --> 01:31:34,200
–Thank God. Thank God.
–What's wrong?

988
01:31:34,280 --> 01:31:36,920
–Help! Help!
–It's OK.

989
01:31:36,960 --> 01:31:41,560
–I thought she was going to hurt me.
–It's over. We have Martin.

990
01:31:41,600 --> 01:31:43,640
You're in deep shit.

991
01:31:44,200 --> 01:31:46,640
–You have Martin?
–Yeah.

992
01:31:59,800 --> 01:32:01,440
Suicide.

993
01:32:04,360 --> 01:32:06,160
Guilty as hell.
